# ApiTransferSaveRequestTransferType

Transfer modality. If not informed and the receiving institution is a Pix participant, the transfer is via Pix. Otherwise via TED.

**Properties**

| Name | Type   | Required | Description |
| :--- | :----- | :------- | :---------- |
| PIX  | String | ✅       | "PIX"       |
| TED  | String | ✅       | "TED"       |
